name: Parking Puzzle
summary: Parking Puzzle is a fun puzzle game that tests your strategic thinking and problem-solving skills. Players must navigate complex parking lots and park cars without hitting obstacles or other vehicles. As the levels progress, new challenges arise, requiring careful planning and precision. With simple controls and varying difficulty levels, the game is accessible to a wide range of players. Parking Puzzle offers a fun, engaging, and addictive gameplay experience for all puzzle enthusiasts.
